<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Due2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Due,</orth> subst. 1) debt: <cit><quote>to have the d. and forfeit of my bond,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 1, 37</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>here is a note of certain --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 2.2.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. II, 2, 16</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>stop the mouth of present --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 2.2.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. II, 2, 16</bibl></cit><lb />2) that which may be claimed as a right: <cit><quote>his d. writ in my testament,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1183" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1183</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to eat the world's d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 1.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. I, 14</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. son 1.31.12" default="NO" valid="yes">31, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 1.39.8" default="NO" valid="yes">39, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 1.46.13" default="NO" valid="yes">46, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 1.69.3" default="NO" valid="yes">69, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 1.69.3" default="NO" valid="yes">69, 3</bibl> <bibl n="shak. son 1.69.3" default="NO" valid="yes">69, 3</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mm 3.2.71" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 2, 71</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.334" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 334</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 2.4.43" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 4, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.59" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 59</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.2.116" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 2, 116</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.5.37" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 37</bibl> (<emph>thy d. from me;</emph> cf. 41). <bibl n="shak. h5 3.7.4" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 7, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.120" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 7, 120</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.120" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 7, 120</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.2.91" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 91</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.27" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.1.29" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.1.132" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 1, 132</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.106" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 106</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.2.174" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 174</bibl> <cit><quote>(--s).</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 3.1.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 1, 37</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.4.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 4, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.5.13" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 5, 13</bibl> <cit><quote>(--s).</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 3.6.25" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 6, 25</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. lr 2.4.182" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 4, 182</bibl> <cit><quote>(--s).</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 3.5.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 5, 11</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>give the devil his d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.133" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 133</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.7.127" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 7, 127</bibl>.
